reviewText: One of my favorite Big Game hunting videos! I've had a copy of this video before but the tape got ruined and I was able to replace it with a copy here on Amazon. I have all 5 of Realtree's Classic Hunts videos, which are some of my favorite Realtree videos, but I wonder why Bill Jordan and the rest of the Realtree guys didn't consider making a Classic Hunts 6.
